		<div id="comment_body_64267118"><p>Because every time some tech-lord drops out of college and becomes a success it&rsquo;s fun to talk about.<br>But when Steve Jobs or Bill Gates dropped out of college it was at practically zero risk to themselves or their ability to graduate some day if they wanted to and they both had very real and concrete things going on, not some vague ideas.</p><p>This is really about keeping plebs uneducated before they&rsquo;re exposed to Ayn Rand.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64267118">
